  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/47e1dff306ce4122811018da01cda4ce.poster.avif?t=1761901541\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/47e1dff306ce4122811018da01cda4ce.webm?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/47e1dff306ce4122811018da01cda4ce.mp4?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 ship variations based on 8 historical models. Command your vessel in real-time sea battles, choose your tactics, and form your own fleet as you explore the Caribbean.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/fd86643324e00159628b455b0575f07e.poster.avif?t=1761901541\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/fd86643324e00159628b455b0575f07e.webm?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/fd86643324e00159628b455b0575f07e.mp4?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After cannon fire comes close combat. Board enemy ships and fight on deck, in the hold, and in the captain’s cabin, while your officers and crew battle at your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/7cb417a4a5c2acd5f3192047afb6f4aa.poster.avif?t=1761901541\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/7cb417a4a5c2acd5f3192047afb6f4aa.webm?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/7cb417a4a5c2acd5f3192047afb6f4aa.mp4?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sail freely across ports, hidden coves, trade routes and dangerous patrol zones. Take contracts, hunt treasures, smuggle goods, or simply chart your own path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/940e101cb15c0702567d08a2883b1d9c.poster.avif?t=1761901541\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/940e101cb15c0702567d08a2883b1d9c.webm?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/940e101cb15c0702567d08a2883b1d9c.mp4?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Rufus Monroe, a smuggler whose routine mission near Trinidad and Tobago goes wrong and triggers a struggle with empires, pirates, and shifting loyalties. Your choices shape your crew, your reputation, and your fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So get ready to set sail on the adventure in Corsairs Legacy! Can you survive the dangers of the Caribbean and become a legendary captain, or will you fall at the hands of your enemies? The choice is yours in this game. Corsairs Legacy awaits!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/47e1dff306ce4122811018da01cda4ce.poster.avif?t=1761901541\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/47e1dff306ce4122811018da01cda4ce.webm?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/47e1dff306ce4122811018da01cda4ce.mp4?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 ship variations based on 8 historical models. Command your vessel in real-time sea battles, choose your tactics, and form your own fleet as you explore the Caribbean.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/fd86643324e00159628b455b0575f07e.poster.avif?t=1761901541\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/fd86643324e00159628b455b0575f07e.webm?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/fd86643324e00159628b455b0575f07e.mp4?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After cannon fire comes close combat. Board enemy ships and fight on deck, in the hold, and in the captain’s cabin, while your officers and crew battle at your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/7cb417a4a5c2acd5f3192047afb6f4aa.poster.avif?t=1761901541\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/7cb417a4a5c2acd5f3192047afb6f4aa.webm?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/7cb417a4a5c2acd5f3192047afb6f4aa.mp4?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sail freely across ports, hidden coves, trade routes and dangerous patrol zones. Take contracts, hunt treasures, smuggle goods, or simply chart your own path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/940e101cb15c0702567d08a2883b1d9c.poster.avif?t=1761901541\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/940e101cb15c0702567d08a2883b1d9c.webm?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594880/extras/940e101cb15c0702567d08a2883b1d9c.mp4?t=1761901541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Rufus Monroe, a smuggler whose routine mission near Trinidad and Tobago goes wrong and triggers a struggle with empires, pirates, and shifting loyalties. Your choices shape your crew, your reputation, and your fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So get ready to set sail on the adventure in Corsairs Legacy! Can you survive the dangers of the Caribbean and become a legendary captain, or will you fall at the hands of your enemies? The choice is yours in this game. Corsairs Legacy awaits!</p>",
